Section 1:
132nd MAINE LEGISLATURE
FIRST REGULAR SESSION-2025
Legislative Document No. 186
An Act to Clarify the Public Utilities Commission's Authority to
Establish Time-of-use Pricing for Standard-offer Service
Reference to the Committee on Energy, Utilities and Technology suggested and ordered
printed.
ROBERT B. HUNT
Clerk
Presented by Representative RUNTE of York.
Cosponsored by Senator LAWRENCE of York and
Representative: SACHS of Freeport.
Printed on recycled paper
1 Be it enacted by the People of the State of Maine as follows:
2 Sec. 1. 35-A MRSA §3212, sub-§4-B, as enacted by PL 2005, c. 677, Pt. B, §2, is
3 amended to read:
4 4-B. Demand response and energy efficiency. The commission may incorporate
5 cost-effective demand response, including the use of time-of-use pricing, and energy
6 efficiency into the supply of standard-offer service. The commission shall encourage
7 entities based in this State that are not otherwise either a standard-offer service provider or
8 its affiliate to participate in supplying cost-effective demand response or energy efficiency
9 pursuant to this subsection.
10 Sec. 2. 35-A MRSA §3212, sub-§4-C, as enacted by PL 2005, c. 677, Pt. B, §2, is
11 amended to read:
12 4-C. Authority to establish various contract lengths and terms. For the purpose of
13 providing over a reasonable time period the lowest price for standard-offer service to
14 residential and small commercial customers, the commission, with respect to residential
15 and small commercial standard-offer service, may, in addition to incorporating cost-
16 effective demand response, including the use of time-of-use pricing, and energy efficiency
17 pursuant to subsection 4‑B and to the extent authorized in section 3210‑C, incorporating
18 the energy portion of any contracts entered into pursuant to section 3210‑C, establish
19 various standard-offer service contract lengths and terms.
20 SUMMARY
2211 This bill clarifies that the Public Utilities Commission may incorporate time-of-use
2222 pricing for the supply of standard-offer service.
